data.description: Light, bright and cozy 3bed, 2bath move-in-ready home in near NE Heights! This extremely well cared for home has an updated kitchen with custom cabinets, granite, and all appliances. Open floor plan with no carpet, and lots of thoughtful touches. Updated baths with beautiful tile work, cabinetry and fixtures. Large utility room with lots of room for storage. All appliances stay, this is truly a turn key home! Fenced backyard with storage shed, and a very large lot. Located in a well-established neighborhood with easy freeway access, near schools and shopping!
